vtex_io_page_other_resources.title: Other resources
vtex_io_page_other_resources_community.d: The VTEX Community is an ecosystem where our clients and partners can interact, ask questions, and exchange information among themselves. It's the go-to place to find answers and talk about VTEX products.
vtex_io_page_other_resources_learning_ce: The Learning Center contains courses about specific aspects of the IO platform and Store Framework.
vtex_io_page_other_resources_github.desc: VTEX IO open-source apps and documentation are fully stored in the VTEX Apps Organization on GitHub.
vtex_io_page_other_resources_help_center: The Help Center contains beginner tutorials, reference guides and troubleshooting articles about the VTEX Admin panel.
vtex_io_page_other_resources_support.des: All clients have access to the services provided by our Technical Support team. These specialists are extensively prepared to give you the best experience possible when solving your tickets. To contact them, you need to open a ticket to VTEX support.
